%E4%BE%8B"><span class="toc-text">3. 全选文本框案例</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-4"><a class="toc-link" href="#4-%E8%B4%AD%E7%89%A9%E8%BD%A6%E5%8A%A0%E5%87%8F%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C"><span class="toc-text">4. 购物车加减操作</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#3-%E9%AB%98%E9%98%B6%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0"><span class="toc-text">3. 高阶函数</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#1-%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E8%A1%A8%E8%BE%BE%E5%BC%8F"><span class="toc-text">1. 函数表达式</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#2-%E5%9B%9E%E8%B0%83%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0"><span class="toc-text">2. 回调函数</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#1-%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E8%A1%A8%E8%BE%BE%E5%BC%8F-1"><span class="toc-text">1. 函数表达式:</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#2-%E5%9B%9E%E8%B0%83%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0-1"><span class="toc-text">2. 回调函数:</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#4-this%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1"><span class="toc-text">4. this环境对象</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#5-%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B%E6%80%9D%E6%83%B3"><span class="toc-text">5. 编程思想</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#1-%E6%8E%92%E4%BB%96%E6%80%9D%E6%83%B3"><span class="toc-text">1.排他思想</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#6-Tab%E6%A0%8F%E5%88%87%E6%8D%A2"><span class="toc-text">6. Tab栏切换</span></a><ol class="toc-child"><li class="toc-item toc-level-4"><a class="toc-link" href="#7-%E7%82%B9%E5%87%BB%E9%9A%8F%E6%9C%BA%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87"><span class="toc-text">7. 点击随机显示图片</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-4"><a class="toc-link" href="#8-%E5%90%8C%E6%84%8F%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE%E6%8C%89%E9%92%AE"><span class="toc-text">8. 同意协议按钮</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-4"><a class=